| Missing rate limiting | Added express-rate-limit |
| NoSQL injection risk | Added mongoSanitize |
| XSS vulnerability | Added xss-clean |
| No input validation | Added validateQueryParams middleware |
| No error handling | Added comprehensive try-catch and error middleware |
| Unbounded payload | Added 10MB size limit |
| No CORS control | Added CORS middleware with whitelist |
| No request tracking | Added UUID request IDs |
| Error info leakage | Conditional error messages (hide in production) |

